U||[Christmas Greetings to Rheinhart Kleiner]
U||By H. P. Lovecraft
U||St. John, whose art sublimely shines
U||In liquid odes and melting lines,
U||Let Theobald his regard express
U||In verse of lesser loveliness.
U||As now in regal state appear
U||The festive hours of Yuletide cheer,
U||My strongest wish is that you may
U||Feel ev’ry blessing of the day!
